description: With pre-made meatballs and lashings of sticky hoisin sauce, this tasty stir-fry recipe is ready in a flash.
name: Speedy Meatball & Veg Stir-Fry Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Add vegetables and cook for 3 minutes or until tender. Add noodles and remaining sauce. Cook, tossing, for 2 minutes or until heated through. Serve sprinkled with onion.
